data.description: Come view this beautiful home located in Dallas ISD only 25 minutes from downtown Dallas, TX. Welcoming 5 bedroom, 3 bath home with lots of curb appeal is ready for you to call your own! This open floor-plan offers an inviting living room with laminate floors and a large kitchen with plenty of cabinetry perfect for hosting family and friends.  Oversized master suite features a walk in closet. Bathroom has a separate shower and a huge bathtub. Large secondary bathrooms with a flex space upstairs ideal for a gameroom. This home has a spacious backyard full of possibilities.  Don't miss out on this property schedule your appointment today!!
